						               													<description>BUTTON MASHERS! is a fast-paced, pocket-sized card game for 2 players! Combo punches and kicks while trying to avoid your opponents attacks!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Great to take on the go or for a quick break between larger games, your luck and guessing skills will be put to the test! Guess correctly, and avoid damage. Guess wrong, and you'll take a foot to the face! Don't let your health reach zero!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Variable rules make it easy to adjust the game for all ages! Make it a simple guessing game, or change it up, and make it a game about reading your opponent's moves, or make up your own rules!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players each have an identical deck of various punches and kicks. After deciding who goes first, the defending player guesses whether the next card to be revealed will be a high(&amp;uarr;), mid, or low(&amp;darr;) attack. If they guess correctly, they take no damage and become the new attacker. However, if they guess wrong, they take the damage listed on the card and must guess again until they make a correct guess.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;For more player control, have the attacking player select which card to put face down instead of just flipping the top card of the deck.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players start with 25 life. First to reach 0 loses and gives their best cry of defeat!&amp;#10;Ready... FIGHT ON!!!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
